description: [Best on Shuffle] Hours and hours and hours of tracks including the best of old school rap, underground hip hop, rare tracks, mixtapes, freestyle, and a little bit of smooth R&B. Some outliers but hope they fit. Adding as I discover and probably a little skewed towards East Coast (sorry).
